Case 1:20-cr-00330-PAE Document 765 Filed 08/10/22 Page 85 of 95 2823 LCIAMAX2ps

1 THE COURT: And then there was one more heading, that had that errant "Two" in it. Oh, page 52, instruction 37, that heading also has the word "Two" in it for some reason.
2 MR. EVERDELL: Yes, your.
3 THE COURT: Verdict sheet.
4 MR. EVERDELL: Your Honor, the edits here are just to track changes we've adopted elsewhere. So as to Count One, "conspiracy to entice an individual under the age of 17 to travel."
5 MR. ROHRBACH: That's fine, your Honor.
6 THE COURT: OK. "An individual." Right. All right. So Count One, we'll adopt that and add "under the age of 17."
7 MR. ROHRBACH: This is actually in Count One also, should be "individuals," plural, I think, in light of the changes we've made?
8 THE COURT: Right. It's a conspiracy count.
9 MR. ROHRBACH: Yes, your Honor.
10 THE COURT: OK, Mr. Everdell.
11 MR. EVERDELL: Count Two, the same thing.
12 THE COURT: Sorry. I just wanted your adoption, "conspiracy to entice individuals under the age."
13 MR. EVERDELL: Yes, your Honor.
14 THE COURT: So we'll cut "an" and make it plural.
15 MR. EVERDELL: Yes, your Honor.
16 THE COURT: Go ahead.

SOUTHERN DISTRICT REPORTERS, P.C. (212) 805-0300

DOJ-OGR-00014389
